{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Game</strong></h2>Trials of Argolis is a <strong>First-Person meele combat Bossrush</strong> set in Ancient Greece mixed with some fantasy elements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Gameplay</strong></h2>Trials of Argolis combines First-Person movement with <strong>fast paced melee combat requiring quick reflexes</strong> and well timed reactions, playing with a controller is recommended.<br>After defeating a Boss you'll be rewarded with Trial-Medals which you can use to improve different physical attributes.<br>There are <strong>6 difficulty settings</strong> to choose from ranging from very forgiving to brutally difficult <strong>including a Perma-Death mode</strong> for the ultimate challenge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your Opponents</strong></h2>The game features <strong>15 unique Bossfights</strong> inlcuding one secret fight. The fights require your full attention if you want to succeed but vary in difficulty.<br>The Bosses do not need to be defeated in any particular order with a few exceptions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Environments</strong></h2>You'll visit <strong>four different environments</strong> over the duration of the game which also vary in time of day.<br>After overcoming an opponent you are free to explore their sometimes quite expansive arenas.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Please Note</strong></h2>This game supports Mouse and Keyboard, Dualshock 4 Controller and Xbox One Controller. Support for any other controllers cannot be guaranteed.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Agora Guard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1453460/83a964eab1cae22a6d4348fb74f32fd120f5d3ee.jpg"},{"name":"Themistocles the Strategos","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1453460/39f2c4cb7fd56687416efc79efefb1822f0de96a.jpg"},{"name":"The Torches of Galenos","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images